name: Ten Vintage Style Teacup Pendants
description:
Supercute set of teacup pendants. These are a printed flat steel with epoxy over the top. Just Lovely! Perfect for making into necklaces for your shop or friends! Each pendant is approx 3.5cm big. Great quality and you won't find these anywhere else! They are brand new. 
Because you are buying ten pendants, they are cheaper than if you just buy two!
